Package com.dyuproject.openid.ext

Interface Summary
Extension Extension for openid which provides the ability to exchange information with the user's openid provider.
Extension.Exchange Puts outgoing params and parses them accordingly if a response is available from the user's openid provider.
 

Class Summary
AbstractExtension Base class for extensions
AxSchemaExtension AxSchema Extension for http://www.axschema.org/types/ - see also http://openid.net/specs/openid-attribute-exchange-1_0-05.html
AxSchemaExtension.AbstractExchange Base class for an axschema exchange which requires a namespace for each field.
AxSchemaExtension.SimpleExchange SimpleExchange - exchanges a key with a value from the user's openid provider.
EmailResolver Resolves the url from a given email address.
SRegExtension Simple Registration Extension See http://openid.net/specs/openid-simple-registration-extension-1_1-01.html
SRegExtension.SimpleExchange SimpleExchange - parses the value denoted by "openid.sreg.$alias = value".
